title: Hour 1 - Ross Tucker (06-30-20)
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Ross Tucker (06-30-20)
description:
Ross Tucker tells Dan that the start of the NFL on time will depend on these next 3 to 4 weeks. Ross says it is important that the NBA and MLB restarts go well. Ross tells Dan that the question is will the NFL end on time?
